            "title": "Genetic Variation and Population Structure in Big Brown Bats (Eptesicus fuscus ): Is Female Dispersal Important?",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Maarten J.",
                    "lastName": "Vonhof"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
